Package: xdvir
Type: Package
Title: Render DVI Files
Version: 0.1-0
Authors@R: person("Paul", "Murrell", email = "paul@stat.auckland.ac.nz",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Paul Murrell <paul@stat.auckland.ac.nz>
Description: Functions to read DVI files, as produced from TeX documents,
             and render them within R.
Depends: R (>= 4.3.0), grid
SystemRequirements: A TeX distribution such as TeX Live, fonttools
Imports: grDevices, hexView (>= 0.3-4), xml2, systemfonts (> 0.1.1)
License: GPL-3
